								ElastiCache Replication for Memcached
								
			- Memcached Clusters can have 1-4- nodes.
			
		
	Horizontal Scaling - Add/remove nodes from the cluster.
	Vertical Scaling - By Larger/smaller node type.
			  - Scale up process : - create a new cluster with the new node type.
			  - Update your applications to use the new clusters endpoints
			  - Delete the old cluster.					
